s which are fractionally\n$3$-colorable. This disproves a conjecture of Gimbel, K\\\"{u}ndgen, Li, and\nThomassen (2019).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 May 2022 09:03:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-18"}
